{"tid":2130971,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"今日一個手足被判18個月刑期，僅僅因為佢嘅車尾箱有棒球棍。","createTime":"2020-07-29T13:35:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T18:50:07.000Z","uid":100155,"like":22,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"5a2140658bd446f1ed8550b4f3a9a90760e31835","tid":2130971,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T13:35:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gy0Ddq2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgy0Ddq2.png&h=76d694b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日紅官蘇文隆又判左一個手足18個月刑期，僅僅因為佢嘅車尾箱有棒球棍。<br />\n<br />\n無數爭取民主嘅手足因為紅官嘅人治判決<br />\n而落得喺牢獄渡過青春嘅下場<br />\n<br />\n希望有人可以將紅官list譯做英文推上國際一定要推到天下制裁。<br />\n黑警 紅官 缺一不可 <br />\n<br />\n紅官list大合集（中文）： <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CCDCXHulO3h/?igshid=1h5x2gen3co49\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCCDCXHulO3h%2F%3Figshid%3D1h5x2gen3co49&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6cF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=764eeab1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCCDCXHulO3h%2F%3Figshid%3D1h5x2gen3co49&h=6e2b9540\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CCDCXHulO3h/?igshid=1h5x2gen3co49</a><br />\n個page仲有其他兩個合集<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SMcqCSF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSMcqCSF.png&h=38289ae4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a1a7ca74daae90535b12b77a64f92693ed6261c","tid":2130971,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T13:36:08.000Z","msg":"突發！元朗要記者！有國安狗咬人！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2130898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2130898</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6cdb56ed75eefc1f8f716c99ff17c5de2cf552d0","tid":2130971,"uid":124134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T13:39:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/no